{
  "texts": [
    "Correspondingly, the whole episode data is used for each PPO update.",
    "Weight initialization is proven to significantly affecthe training process.",
    "(LeCun et al., 2012) Thus, the weights are initialized using Xavier Uniform Distribution.",
    "(Glorot & Bengio, 2010) Xavier Uniform Distribution is also used by (Mirhoseini et al., 2021) and (Yu et al., 2021) and has proven to deliver a good starting point for optimization in their use cases.",
    "The maximum episode length is set to 3000 time steps to avoid too large episodes."
  ]
}